    <item>
      <title>中国塑料热潮或将引发又一贸易难题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/china-s-plastics-boom-is-set-to-create-another-trade-headache</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在国内需求疲软的情况下，中国塑料供应激增，面临溢出威胁，这对世界其他地区构成新的贸易挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/china-s-plastics-boom-is-set-to-create-another-trade-headache</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 23:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国通胀降温或将提振韩国央行政策转向押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/south-korea-s-inflation-cools-more-than-expected-toward-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在韩国央行召开重要会议之前，通胀放缓幅度超过预期，这进一步表明价格压力正在缓解，这可能使政策制定者在未来几个月放松限制性政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/south-korea-s-inflation-cools-more-than-expected-toward-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元上涨，股市因美国大选押注而波动：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于上周特朗普与拜登的辩论后，交易员们开始权衡特朗普再次当选总统的可能性，美元上涨，亚洲股市窄幅波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 22:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
